{"tid":480264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環運垃圾老伯伯手推車上不小心掉了一包垃圾 立即被食環票控","createTime":"2017-11-26T03:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T09:36:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe30a495120bb29321992edc8e699a932053529","tid":480264,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:51:45.000Z","msg":"平時係街頭上，大家都會見過為我哋清潔街頭嘅工友。每次有咩大型活動過後，佢哋嘅工作量往往大增，但佢哋仍不辭勞苦咁為我哋潔淨環境。<br />\n<br />\n而喺上個月嘅中環街頭，相中嘅呢位伯伯推住一車垃圾，無發覺有一包垃圾喺垃圾車上面趺咗落嚟。此時有三位身穿便衣嘅食環，拎著相機，畀伯伯睇佢唔小心趺咗一袋垃圾嘅照片，然後再發出告票。<br />\n<br />\n亂拋垃圾定額罰款本來係針對垃圾蟲嘅懲罰，而此刻負責處理垃圾嘅工友卻被告亂拋垃圾。法律不外乎人情，伯伯並非有心所為，如果可以作出善意嘅提醒，唔係一個更好嘅處理方法咩？<br />\n<br />\n註：照片非案發當時。原圖及資料感謝Tomomi Wong授權使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/115115_c98fbe969bdfc0d1eb88fb94c9e24318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F115115_c98fbe969bdfc0d1eb88fb94c9e24318.jpg&h=a13c8bee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1094eeacf67232ab6d6658e71ad40035ab44e2de","tid":480264,"uid":78149,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"食環狗 屌你老母"},{"pid":"451fa411340b5797aecc4569c2bc3b7a246eafaf","tid":480264,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"可以著便衣嘅咩"},{"pid":"876ec31daa1765b272ad0b2cba98b41b638cd996","tid":480264,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:53:43.000Z","msg":"有無張發票睇下，有既我想幫下呀伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af779bc64b3c07cdd80e5b29e6a0b77fd74a75f","tid":480264,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"食環狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744458e18171995e737ef626518179253495f84d","tid":480264,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"應該有得打"},{"pid":"a189954bde2c78f9f73abb0b0373c238f7c336e6","tid":480264,"uid":38757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"點解食環經常性要做呢D 咁既小動作?....係咪真係票控方面有quota 交數...<br />\n唔票控唔得?"},{"pid":"0380d30ea35b2afcdc8186460b324a6c5d314f4f","tid":480264,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41da298fe0bf56a842f4051899bc42d47317cf05","tid":480264,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解食環經常性要做呢D 咁既小動作?....係咪真係票控方面有quota 交數...<br />\n唔票控唔得?</blockquote><br />\n有前食環署人員向本報透露，署方管理層一直以檢控數字多寡以顯示管治能力，並與其他地區作比較，博取升職表現，故前線人員每月被逼「跑數」，長期受壓，部份人甚至每月要「上繳」雙位數的告票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170907/57177655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170907%2F57177655&d=r%2F49uCi42EMBuif2e4VsKDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0dc2fe10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170907%2F57177655&h=1ed0cc9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170907/57177655</a>"},{"pid":"5e7b1f75156f578cacb634247bea7f1f89b29b93","tid":480264,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"目光留左係部解款車度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc05568584557da3c705db83fadf705a55da586","tid":480264,"uid":41658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"廢老對食環,連登矛盾之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778822b228620d0c3b11001c80988980d3172c00","tid":480264,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/132427_695